Warts Warthogs are popular, but some are more famous than others. Here are our favourite warts
A-10 Thunderbolt BBBRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRTTTTTT The A-10 is famously ugly, and brutal, and its warthog nickname probably comes from the look of the aircraft from the front. Halo Warthog Master Chief&rsquo;s preferred mode of transport ATV The British Army use the Warthog All Terrain Vehicle (ATV), a compact tracked troop carrier https://www.eliteukforces.info/uksf-gear/warthog/
Pumbaa Too annoying? Hakuna matata&hellip;
